            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>
                Dream X was born from a simple observation: social media has incredible power to connect 
                people, but it often pulls us away from the things that truly matter. We asked ourselves, 
                "What if there was a platform that helped people grow instead of just scroll?"
            </p>
            <p>
                That's when Dream X was created — a social network specifically designed for productive 
                people who want to share their passions, build meaningful skills, and inspire others along 
                the way.
            </p>
        </div>

